title: King of Spirit Beast
description: King of Spirit Beast Manhua It all started with a whale, whose cultivation was all about swallowing things. This was a fantasy world crowded with spiritual monsters. Fan Lingxiao, the chief of Sky Vagabond, grew a little catfish into an all-devouring whale and beame a world-famous spirit master. However, the whale somehow failed in a combat, and turned into a cruel zombie whale which swallowed Fan Lingxiao. When he woke up, everything had change… The All-Devouring Whale The Whale Shallowing The Whole World 鯤吞天下
alternative_titles: The Whale Shallowing The Whole World
